{"id":279279,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/【首发】广东开平村民反贪示威-堵让子弹飞碉/","date":"2013-02-15T19:30:24Z","modified":"2013-02-15T19:30:24Z","title":"【首发】广东开平村民反贪示威 堵“让子弹飞”碉楼村大门 (2视频/19图)","content":"<p><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div><span>2013</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span><span>2</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>14</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">广东江门开平市塘口镇，著名的碉楼立园旅游景区，数百名村民在入口处进行围堵示威，抗议村干部贪污腐化。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">村民拉起多张大横幅，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">上面写着：「终止不合理的合同</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">废除权力大过法律</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">还我村民权力」、「追究国家征地补偿款项」、「还我土地」等，并敲锣打鼓大肆张扬，</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">大批警察在场戒备和疏导交通。下午，警方清场，</span><span>5</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">名村民被捕。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">村民表示，村干部私下与景区签了份不合理的合同，侵占村民的血汗钱，村民多次到镇政府上访未果，只好堵塞景区大门，希望能讨一个公道。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">开平</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">碉楼立园景区是著名电影“让子弹飞”和“一代宗师”的拍摄地，亦是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">世界文化遗产之一。</span><span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--sOQKSOcv3g/UR4HAWlkR9I/AAAAAAAAS0c/BT7rtdcVuvQ/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"383\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/--sOQKSOcv3g/UR4HAWlkR9I/AAAAAAAAS0c/BT7rtdcVuvQ/s640/1.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-GH2pzils0N8/UR4HBgaW--I/AAAAAAAAS0k/ZQD1NGqdNZc/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"481\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-GH2pzils0N8/UR4HBgaW--I/AAAAAAAAS0k/ZQD1NGqdNZc/s640/2.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-gFjgN7QAcik/UR4HCy94SqI/AAAAAAAAS0s/XL-yqp0sLYs/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogs